thread.title: Lexi Thompson wins LPGA Tour event in South Korea

title: Lexi Thompson wins LPGA Tour event in South Korea
text:
> Florida Lexi Thompson wins LPGA Tour event in South Korea Lexi Thompson of the United States walks on the sixth green during the final round of the LPGA KEB Hana Bank Championship golf tournament at Sky72 Golf Club in Incheon, South Korea, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015.
